      "name": "Approval gate for a not-yet-approved user",
      "content": "<ol><li>Sign in as a user who has applied but isn't approved yet.</li></ol><p><strong>Expected:</strong> You land on the /waiting page rather than the full app.</p><p><strong>Result:</strong> ☐ Pass ☐ Fail — Notes: ______________________________</p>",
