      "name": "Approved user reaches the app",
      "content": "<ol><li>Sign in as an approved user.</li></ol><p><strong>Expected:</strong> You get straight into the app.</p><p><strong>Result:</strong> ☐ Pass ☐ Fail — Notes: ______________________________</p>",
