      "name": "Beta feedback earns Pro and a badge",
      "content": "<ol><li>Go to /feedback and submit the beta feedback form.</li></ol><p><strong>Expected:</strong> You're granted a year of Pro and a Founding User badge.</p><p><strong>Result:</strong> ☐ Pass ☐ Fail — Notes: ______________________________</p>",
