      "content": "<ol><li>Open the bug report dialog.</li><li>Type a short description (at least 3 characters).</li><li>Press Send.</li></ol><p><strong>Expected:</strong> The report sends and a success message appears without covering the Send button.</p><p><strong>Result:</strong> ☐ Pass ☐ Fail — Notes: ______________________________</p>",
