      "id": "mtp-sc-13-1",
      "name": "Same outline on desktop and web",
      "content": "<ol><li>Open an outline in the desktop app.</li><li>Open the same account/outline on the web.</li></ol><p><strong>Expected:</strong> The outline looks and behaves the same in both places.</p><p><strong>Result:</strong> ☐ Pass ☐ Fail — Notes: ______________________________</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "mtp-area-crossplatform",
      "childrenIds": [],
